# vecto :construction: :sparkles: :art:
# @0.7.1
# A JavaScript Mini Library to deal with N-dimensional arrays.


## <b> What's new </b>

* ndarray -> Ndarray
* <a href='#fill'>fill</a> method
* <a href='#max'>max</a> & <a href='#min'>min</a> methods
